# About This Lab
**Objective:** In this lab, we will perform a number of transformations on dataframes. This will provide exposure to the API, and some experience in using it. We will cover a number of common techniques, but will not attempt to cover all of the API, or try to illustrate every possible technique. The API is too large for that.
